Shohei Ohtani is going to likely get a record contract next offseason. Justin Verlander and Max Scherzer are pals now. The Yankees have some question marks. The Orioles and their young roster are hoping to fight for the playoffs this year. Those are the big storylines on “The Show” podcast this week with Joel Sherman and Jon Heyman. Orioles GM Mike Elias is their guest as he breaks down the Orioles roster, offseason and playoff aspirations.